    &lt;Title&gt;Waiting times. Lack of transparency.&lt;/Title&gt;
    &lt;ScreenName&gt;R.K&lt;/ScreenName&gt;
    &lt;CommentText&gt;I was referred to a consultant and got a quick appointment. The consultant I was given operated on someone I know which Is good as he was highly recommended. I was put on the waiting list for THR in Mar 2019. A few weeks later I went to the Hip/Knee school to learn about the recovery procedures. Everyone was told the waiting list for surgery for THR was 18 weeks. Covid 19 came about Mar 2020 and as of Sept 2020 I am still waiting. It appears that the 18 weeks comes from the government guidelines. Unfortunately it was not 18 weeks. Such a shame as I am a great advocate of the NHS.  &lt;/CommentText&gt;
